OL,6,FA 'calculating' man from Churchdown
OL,7,Fwho sexually assaulted a woman while
OL,8,Fshe was trying to sleep has been
OL,9,Fjailed.
OL,11,FAlex Russ, aged 34 and of Craven
OL,12,FDrive, pleaded guilty to sexually
OL,13,Fassaulting a woman and secretly
OL,14,Ffilming two others.
OL,16,FHe had previously pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Fthree counts of sexual assault against
OL,18,Fone woman and two counts of voyeurism
OL,19,Fagainst two further women.
