OL,6,FRuss was sentenced to six years and
OL,7,Ffive months in prison when he appeared
OL,8,Fat Gloucester Crown Court.
OL,10,FIn 2015, while staying at the home of
OL,11,Fa woman, she had started to go to
OL,12,Fsleep when Russ pulled her pyjama
OL,13,Fbottoms down and sexually assaulted
OL,14,Fher. She was able to stop him and
OL,15,Fchallenge his behaviour.
OL,17,FOn another two occasions, Russ got
OL,18,Finto bed with her while she again
OL,19,Ftried to sleep and he sexually
OL,20,Fassaulted her.
