OL,4,Cassaults and secretly filming women
OL,6,FThe court heard that the day before
OL,7,Fthe first incident, Russ had used his
OL,8,Ftablet device to search for sleep
OL,9,Fdisorders involving sexual behaviour.
OL,11,FRuss also admitted to secretly filming
OL,12,Fwomen without their knowledge or
OL,13,Fconsent.
OL,15,FOne incident saw him set up a camera
OL,16,Fphone in a washbag and leave it in a
OL,17,Fbathroom, where he was able to film a
OL,18,Fwoman before and after she showered.
