OL,4,Cassaults and secretly filming women
OL,6,FAnother time involved a camera hidden
OL,7,Fin an alarm clock which he set up in a
OL,8,Froom being used by a different woman.
OL,10,FAlthough he initially denied the
OL,11,Foffences, Russ pleaded guilty on the
OL,12,Ffirst day of trial in October 2023.
OL,14,FAs well as being jailed, Russ has been
OL,15,Fput on the Sex Offenders Register for
OL,16,Flife, and restraining orders have been
OL,17,Fput in place to protect the women.
