OL,6,FThe officer who led the investigation
OL,7,Ffrom Gloucestershire Constabulary
OL,8,Fsaid: "I believe the fact that he
OL,9,Fsearched for sleep disorders shows
OL,10,Fthat Russ's actions were premeditated.
OL,12,F"He is a calculating individual.
OL,14,F"We would like to commend all three
OL,15,Fvictims who came forward to speak to
OL,16,Fofficers and support police action.
