OL,6,F"Two of the victims felt that, at the
OL,7,Ftime of initial reporting, they did
OL,8,Fnot want to proceed with the
OL,9,Finvestigation. This is the choice of
OL,10,Fany victim of any crime, and their
OL,11,Fdecisions were respected at the time.
OL,13,F"They came back to police at a later
OL,14,Fstage, when they felt able to support
OL,15,Fthe case.
OL,17,F"It cannot be underestimated the
OL,18,Fstrength that each of these victims
OL,19,Fhas shown in providing the evidence to
OL,20,Ftake this forward."
